{"word":"Ashdod","slug":"ashdod","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ashdod</b> <a href=\"#/H795\">H795</a><br/><a href=\"#/H796\">H796</a> <br/> A city of the Philistines<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=13&verse=3'>Jos 13:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=6&verse=17'>1Sa 6:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=3&verse=9'>Amo 3:9</a><br/> Anakim inhabit<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=11&verse=22'>Jos 11:22</a><br/> Assigned to Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=15&verse=47'>Jos 15:47</a><br/> Dagon's temple in, in which the ark was deposited<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=5&verse=12'>1Sa 5:12</a><br/> Conquest of, by Uzziah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=6'>2Ch 26:6</a><br/> Conquest of, by Tartan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=20&verse=1'>Isa 20:1</a><br/> People of, conspire against the Jews<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=4&verse=8'>Neh 4:8</a><br/> Jews intermarry with<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=13&verse=24'>Neh 13:24</a><br/> Prophecies concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=25&verse=20'>Jer 25:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=1&verse=8'>Amo 1:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=3&verse=15'>Amo 3:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=36&chapter=2&verse=4'>Zep 2:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=9&verse=6'>Zec 9:6</a><br/> Called Azotus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=8&verse=40'>Act 8:40</a>"}]}